This template generates one or more links for the Japanese {{nihongo4|[[National Bibliography Number]]|全国書誌番号}} or JPNO of publications. The {{nihongo4|Japanese National Bibliography|日本全国書誌}} is maintained by the {{nihongo4|[[:en:National Diet Library|National Diet Library]]|国立国会図書館}} of Japan. It takes up to nine parameters. It is intended as an alternative, when the book in question does not appear in the [[:en:OCLC|Online Computer Library Center]].

The template can also be used inside the {{para|id}} parameter of the various {{cite xxx}} citation templates.

Example #1:
*Usage: <code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}|21005395<nowiki>}}</nowiki></code>
*Renders as: {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|21005395}}

Note: Unlike the NDL bib ID, e.g., [https://id.ndl.go.jp/bib/000008144816/eng https://id.ndl.go.jp/bib/000008144816/eng], the JPNO is designed to also be used outside of NDL, e.g., {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230617084354/http://webcatplus.nii.ac.jp/webcatplus/details/book/nbn/21005395.html |title=http://webcatplus.nii.ac.jp/webcatplus/details/book/nbn/21005395.html}} from the ''former'' Webcat Plus by the {{nihongo4|[[National Institute of Informatics]]|国立情報学研究所}}.

==Changes==
JPNO ID links like [https://id.ndl.go.jp/jpno/21005395 https://id.ndl.go.jp/jpno/21005395] redirect to the [[:en:OpenURL|OpenURL]] API.

This API changed in December 2023:<ref>{{cite web |title=Providing Japanese National Bibliography, etc. |url=https://www.ndl.go.jp/en/use/2024renewal/02.html |work=[[:en:National Diet Library|National Diet Library]] |access-date=2024-07-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Integration of the NDL Online and NDL Search web services |url=https://www.ndl.go.jp/en/use/2024renewal/index.html |work=[[:en:National Diet Library|National Diet Library]] |access-date=2024-07-01}}</ref>
* from https://iss.ndl.go.jp/api/openurl where previously the English UI could be accessed by adding <code><nowiki>locale=en</nowiki></code> to the [[:en:Query string|Query string]]
* to https://ndlsearch.ndl.go.jp/api/openurl which in turn redirect to https://ndlsearch.ndl.go.jp/openurl?cs=api_openurl and the English UI can be accessed via https://ndlsearch.ndl.go.jp/en/openurl?cs=api_openurl

This means links are changed:
* from [https://iss.ndl.go.jp/api/openurl?ndl_jpno=21005395&locale=en https://iss.ndl.go.jp/api/openurl?ndl_jpno=21005395&locale=en]
* to [https://ndlsearch.ndl.go.jp/en/openurl?cs=api_openurl&f-ndl_jpno=21005395 https://ndlsearch.ndl.go.jp/en/openurl?cs=api_openurl&f-ndl_jpno=21005395]

